@startuml
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam monochrome true
title Pullout Request State Transition

[*] --> Pending : Employee submits request

Pending --> Approved : Admin approves\n& stock available
Pending --> Rejected : Admin rejects
Pending --> OutOfStock : Insufficient stock

OutOfStock --> Pending : Stock replenished

Approved --> InUse : Supplies pulled out

InUse --> PartiallyReturned : Some items returned
InUse --> FullyReturned : All items returned
InUse --> Consumed : Supplies fully used

PartiallyReturned --> FullyReturned : Remaining returned

Approved --> [*] : No returns needed
Rejected --> [*] : Request denied
FullyReturned --> [*] : Transaction closed
Consumed --> [*] : Transaction closed

Pending : Awaiting approval
Pending : Stock validation needed

Approved : Inventory deducted
Approved : Supplies available

InUse : Supplies being used
InUse : Can track returns

Rejected : Request denied
Rejected : Stock not deducted

@enduml
